∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} {x : ℝ}, 
  (∀ x' ≥ 1, ContinuousAt f x') →
    (∃ z : ℝ → ℝ, ∀ x ≥ 1, (∫ t in 1..x, z t) = ∫ t in 1..x, ((x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t) / (n - 1)! / t ^ n)

∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} {x : ℝ},
  1 ≤ x →
    (∀ t ≥ 1, ContinuousAt f t) →
      ∃ z : ℝ → ℝ,
        (∀ t ∈ Set.Icc 1 x, z t = (x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t / ((n - 1)! * t ^ n)) ∧
          (∫ (t : ℝ) in 1..x, z t = ∫ (t : ℝ) in 1..x, (x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t / ((n - 1)! * t ^ n))

∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} (x : ℝ),
  1 ≤ x →
  ContinuousOn f (Set.Ici 1) →
  let z : ℝ → ℝ := fun t => (x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t / ((n - 1)! * t ^ n) in
  ∀ y : ℝ → ℝ,
    (∀ k : ℕ, k < n → deriv^[k] y 1 = 0) →
    (∀ x, (∏ i in Finset.range n, (x * deriv - i)) y = f x) →
    y x = ∫ t in 1..x, z t

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {n : ℕ} {x : ℝ},
  1 ≤ x →
    ContinuousOn f (Set.Ici 1) →
      y x = ∫ (t : ℝ) in 1..x, (x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t / ((n - 1)! * t ^ n) ↔
        (∀ k : ℕ, k < n → iteratedDerivWithRespectToX k y 1 = 0) ∧
          iteratedDerivWithRespectToX n y = f

∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} {x : ℝ},
  1 ≤ x →
    (∀ t, 1 ≤ t → ContinuousAt f t) →
      ∃ z : ℝ → ℝ, (∀ x, y x = ∫ t in 1..x, z t) ∧ 
        y x = ∫ t in 1..x, ((x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t) / ((n - 1)! * t ^ n)

∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} {y : ℝ → ℝ},
  ContinuousOn f (Set.Ici 1) →
    (∀ x ≥ 1, (∏ i in Finset.range n, (λ δ : ℝ → ℝ, x * (deriv δ)) (Finset.iterate i deriv) y) x = f x) →
      (∀ k < n, deriv^[k] y 1 = 0) →
        ∀ x ≥ 1, y x = ∫ (t : ℝ) in 1..x, (x - t)^(n - 1) * f t / ((n - 1)! * t^n)

∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} {y : ℝ → ℝ},
  (∀ x ≥ 1, ContinuousAt f x) →
    (∀ x ≥ 1, iteratedDeriv n (fun y => x * deriv y x) y = f x) →
      (∀ k < n, iteratedDeriv k y 1 = 0) →
        ∀ x ≥ 1, y x = ∫ (t : ℝ) in 1..x, ((x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t) / (n - 1)! * t ^ (-n)

∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} {y : ℝ → ℝ},
  (∀ x ≥ 1, ContinuousAt f x) →
    (∀ x ≥ 1, (δ ^ n) y x = f x) →
      y 1 = 0 ∧ ∀ k < n, deriv^[k] y 1 = 0 →
        (∀ x ≥ 1, y x = ∫ t in 1..x, ((x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t) / ((n - 1)! * t ^ n))

∀ {n : ℕ} {f : ℝ → ℝ} {y : ℝ → ℝ},
  (∀ x, ContinuousOn f (Set.Ici 1)) →
    (y 1 = 0) →
      (∀ k < n, deriv^[k] y 1 = 0) →
        (∀ x ≥ 1, (iteratedDeriv n (fun x => x * deriv (fun x => x) x) y x) = f x) →
          (∀ x ≥ 1, y x = ∫ t in 1..x, ((x - t) ^ (n - 1) * f t) / ((n - 1) ! * t ^ n))
